### WARNING
### This file changes local development data.
### Creating an order reserves Inventory stock.
### Cancelling an order releases Inventory reservation.
### Inventory API must be running and configured through InventoryApi:BaseUrl.
### Change runId before running the full flow again.

@OrderingApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5172
@InventoryApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5245
@runId = 001

@warehouseId = 1a279d4c-ee02-4c86-bd4d-175f4098a709
@locationId = 38a754af-e46e-4d4e-a014-a8dc68cda9fa
@sku = ARM-BLK

### Health check
GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/health


### Check Inventory stock before order
GET {{InventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/stock/{{sku}}


### List orders
GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders


### Create order and reserve Inventory stock
# @name createOrder
POST {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Test Customer {{runId}}",
  "customerEmail": "test-{{runId}}@example.com",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "a301a968-7477-4db5-bafd-edfb3bd03675",
      "productVariantId": "9572fb9d-f059-401e-9041-7fc75f8cb414",
      "sku": "{{sku}}",
      "productName": "Monitor Arm",
      "variantName": "Black",
      "unitPriceAmountMinor": 6900,
      "currency": "USD",
      "quantity": 2,
      "warehouseId": "{{warehouseId}}",
      "locationId": "{{locationId}}"
    }
  ]
}


### Get created order details
@orderId = {{createOrder.response.body.$.id}}

GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}


### Check Inventory stock after order reservation
GET {{InventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/stock/{{sku}}


### Cancel order and release Inventory reservation
POST {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}/cancel


### Get order details after cancel
GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}


### Check Inventory stock after cancel
GET {{InventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/stock/{{sku}}


### List orders after flow
GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders


### Create invalid order without items should return 400
POST {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Invalid Customer",
  "customerEmail": "invalid@example.com",
  "items": []
}


### Create invalid order with mixed currencies should return 400
POST {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Invalid Customer",
  "customerEmail": "invalid@example.com",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "a301a968-7477-4db5-bafd-edfb3bd03675",
      "productVariantId": "9572fb9d-f059-401e-9041-7fc75f8cb414",
      "sku": "{{sku}}",
      "productName": "Monitor Arm",
      "variantName": "Black",
      "unitPriceAmountMinor": 6900,
      "currency": "USD",
      "quantity": 1,
      "warehouseId": "{{warehouseId}}",
      "locationId": "{{locationId}}"
    },
    {
      "productId": "a301a968-7477-4db5-bafd-edfb3bd03675",
      "productVariantId": "9572fb9d-f059-401e-9041-7fc75f8cb414",
      "sku": "{{sku}}",
      "productName": "Monitor Arm",
      "variantName": "Black",
      "unitPriceAmountMinor": 6900,
      "currency": "EUR",
      "quantity": 1,
      "warehouseId": "{{warehouseId}}",
      "locationId": "{{locationId}}"
    }
  ]
}


### Missing order should return 404
GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000